Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:31.15,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Hidamari no naka nayami mo shirazu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.53,0:22:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sunny spot, blissfully oblivious of worries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So we spent days when you were still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:40.17,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Ikiteita ano hi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why is it only when one loses something,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:48.35,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Nee hito wa itsumo nani ka nakushita toki ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:56.66,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Ari no mama no jibun ni kidzuku no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets to perceive what was actually going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:23:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I wonder if you can hear me \Neven while you're not here anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:23:04.67,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Nee ima wa inai anata kikoeru kashira
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made a promise to carry on living my own way, \Ntherefore you must also, even if for an eternity,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:15.79,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Watashi rashiku ikite yuku to yakusoku suru kara anata wa itsumade mo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:19.35,ROMAJI,,0,0,0,,Miteite ne
