Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi Oka, it's time. \NCome to the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:01:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear? It's raining, all day raining. \NHere it's rainy New York!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All the remaining snow \Nnearly disappeared because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it rains all around the globe today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means{can't hear the first "zessa" word, going with johnny's}, \NI absolutely wanna report it to Coach Munakata!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,About how far I could advance! \NMade it all the way to final round!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And opponent is the most prominent \Nnext American tennis{ world} queen candidate, Belle Mackenzie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what it means? \NAt 18, she is a world-ranker already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell if it was by abilities or luck, but after getting this far, you'll make it to the very end, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When you put it like that, \Nyou're making me uneasy too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Maki, haven't you got sick recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry. Yeah, just a bit. \NThink I might have a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well up to this point. \NGreat job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he said he's looking forward to your return. \NHe knew Hiromi would bring home a medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy, ain't that obvious? \NCoach Munakata, who taught you everything!{/ your honorable tutor!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you should keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, OK! Got you covered!{/ Leave that to me!}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, this is my final match here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I could only make it this far thanks to Coach \Nwalking this way alongside me, in my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why, with all my heart, \NI want to bring back a medal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, that will make Coach \Ncommend me wholeheartedly for once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away this time, Coach.{/ You'll do that for me, won't you, Coach?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, this will be your penalty \Nfor not coming to America!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm doing it!
